h1 {

color: #A68784;

.title-big {
font-size: 100pt;

}
.title-medium {
font-size: 30pt;
border-bottom: solid 1px #253548;
font-weight: 700;
}
.title-medium::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height:6px;
    border-top: 4px solid #253548;
}
.title-big,
.title-medium {
color: #253548;
font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;

}

table 
{
    background-color: white !important;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #A68784 !important;
    border-top: 1px solid transparent !important;
    border-left: 1px solid transparent  !important;
    border-right: 1px solid transparent  !important;
}

table thead
{
border-color: transparent !important
}

table thead tr
{
border-color: transparent !important
}

table thead tr td 
{   
background-color: #A68784 !important;
color: white !important; 
text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid white !important;
    border-top: 1px solid white  !important;
    border-left: 1px solid #A68784 !important;
    border-right: 2px solid white !important;
}

table thead tr td:first-child {
    background-color: white !important;
    color: #A68784 !important;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #A68784 !important;
    border-top: 1px solid white !important;
    border-left: 1px solid white !important;
    border-right: 1px solid #A68784 !important;
    text-align: left;
}

table tbody tr td 
{   
    border-top: 1px solid transparent !important;
    border-left: 1px solid transparent !important;
    border-right: 1px solid transparent !important;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent  !important;
}
